{"tid":2195151,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"中國八月出口增9.5% 勝預期","createTime":"2020-09-09T03:51:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-10T11:56:15.000Z","uid":66087,"like":3,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"9e087f237801157acd430080f7612f07054f5679","tid":2195151,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T03:51:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.msn.com/zh-hk/money/news/中國八月出口增9-5-勝預期/ar-BB18NFUD?li=AAavKXB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.msn.com%2Fzh-hk%2Fmoney%2Fnews%2F%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%85%AB%E6%9C%88%E5%87%BA%E5%8F%A3%E5%A2%9E9-5-%E5%8B%9D%E9%A0%90%E6%9C%9F%2Far-BB18NFUD%3Fli%3DAAavKXB&d=Yvf7L03l0%2FKFASkGPCPwg4eNTHq1rgEicHo%2BkVhR8rs%3D&h=0d987598\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.msn.com/zh-hk/money/news/中國八月出口增9-5-勝預期/ar-BB18NFUD?li=AAavKXB</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n受防疫物品出口支撐，及外需逐步改善帶動，中國8月出口表現勝預期。<br />\n<br />\n以美元計，中國8月出口按年增9.5%，較7月高2.3個百分點；增速創2019年3月以來最高；進口則按年降2.1%，較7月再回落0.7個百分點，遠遜市場預期。<br />\n<br />\n有分析人士預計，接下來數月中國出口仍可保持較強勢的正增長，而進口在內需復甦帶動下，有望重現正增長。<br />\n<br />\n8月中國實現貿易順差589.3億美元，較7月減少34億美元。以人民幣計價，8月中國出口按年增11.6%，進口微降0.5%，實現貿易順差4165.9億元人民幣。<br />\n<br />\n今年累計首8月，以美元計，出口按年降2.3%，進口降5.2%，貿易順差2890.6億美元。"},{"pid":"f6e575ae001e210794c2a666133e777ee04f7639","tid":2195151,"uid":66087,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T03:52:21.000Z","msg":"今次真係比支那起死回生 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />..."},{"pid":"bac136d89b6c727845d5a87aad91fba15604b118","tid":2195151,"uid":78039,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T03:52:43.000Z","msg":"內循環都贏"},{"pid":"72732226b0fd0efe10a1618da214295a743d1f4c","tid":2195151,"uid":345502,"like":15,"dislike":4,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"f6e575ae001e210794c2a666133e777ee04f7639","tid":2195151,"uid":66087,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T03:52:21.000Z","msg":"今次真係比支那起死回生 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />..."},"citedBy":1,